    "title": "SeaKing Bait Board HH-14 (625mm x 390mm)",
    "body_html": "<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>SeaKing HH-14</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>The SeaKing HH-14 is a compact version of our SeaKing H-10, offering the luxury of built in two cup holders, </span><span>one on each side. This model also features a knife compartment and a spacious sink compartment. </span><span>Designed as a high-end board, the SeaKing HH-14 is suitable for both large and small vessels. It is </span><span>constructed from premium composite materials and includes a UV-resistant PE plastic cutting board.</span><strong></strong></p>",
